*Generale* su izdavale naredbe da se ukopaju trupe. (Generals issued orders to bury the troops.)

Vojska je bila podređena *generale* koji je vodio bitku. (The army was subordinated to the general who led the battle.)

U nastavku bitke, *generale* je odlučio da prekine borbu. (In the continuation of the battle, the general decided to stop the fight.)

*Generale* i njegova vojska su se borili neumorno. (The general and his army fought tirelessly.)

*Generale* je bilo odgovorno za odbranu zemlje. (The general was responsible for defending the country.)